title: 2017 Week 3 Recap
itunes:title: 2017 Week 3 Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler & Gregg Rosenthal,– recap the week 3 games including the Jacksonville Jaguars huge win in London, Green Bay’s overtime comeback, and the Jets pulling their first win. The heroes also get you up to date with all things around the NFL concluding Week 3.
